              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " A lithium fluoride target was used to measure the",
                "absolute cross section of the Li7(p,alpha)He4 reaction",
                "at 0.880 MeV.",
                " The thickness of a LiF target was determined by",
                "measuring the width of the gamma-ray yield curve at",
                "the 0.872-MeV F-19(p,alpha+gamma)0-16 resonance."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The absolute cross section at 880 keV calculated",
                "using knowledge of the stopping cross section",
                "of LiF for 88O-keV protons"
              ]
            }
          ],
